	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=42869><span id= >phynixice</span></a><br><span id=notbold>1 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Look, we all go through times that seem like we will never get to the next lvl but trust me it passes. <br> I'd like to put my 2cp into the AoE topic. AoE are very usefull in a good grp. When your tank pulls 2 to 4 mobs and you have 3 maybe 4 mellee types in grp they can engage 1 on 1 the mobs while you AoE the mobs to death with no chance of agro. I like to do this when the grp is getting steady yet boring exp to spice it up! It works very well for me. I must say that the dd AoE spells i like much better because the mobs dont have to stay in the area for an extended period of time.<br> <br><br>Phynix Spellfury<br>lvl 32 wizard<br>The Enhanced</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
